1. Kinematic plot of a sigle parameter from a particular Minitree root file, type:
> python KinematicPlot.py /PATH/TO/MINITREE/Minitree.root --param="pt4l_fsr" --weight="weight_couplings" --nbin=100 --min=0 --max=400 -o=./result
This will produce a weighted plot of the parameter pt4l_fsr with the weight weight_couplings with 100 bins and x axis ranging from 0 to 400(GeV)

2. Kinematic plot of multiple parameters from multiple Minitree root files, first prepare
A. input file containing the list of minitree root files, with the first line indicating the directory of the root files, e.g. input.txt
B. param file containing the list of parameters to be plotted, with the first line indicating the weight to be used; include the number of bins x minimum and x maximum separated by parenthesis after the parameter
then type:
> python KinematicPlots.py input.txt --param=param.txt -o=./result
